COHPStartEnergy -15
COHPEndEnergy 15
basisSet pbeVaspFit2015
includeOrbitals  s p d
basisFunction H 1s
basisFunction O 2s 2p
basisFunction Al 3s 3p
basisFunction Ni 3d 4s 4p
# Al atom with O atom
cohpBetween atom 39 and atom 25 orbitalWise
# Ni atom with O atom
cohpBetween atom 47 and atom 25 orbitalWise
cohpBetween atom 48 and atom 25 orbitalWise
